      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>HELLMAN-Aviva. The conference of Presidents of Major American Jewish Organizations mourns the passing of Aviva Hellman, widow of its distinguished founding executive vice chairman, Yehuda Hellman. We pray that the family will be comforted among the mourners of Zion and Jerusalem. Ronald S. Lauder, Chairman Malcolm Hoenlein, Executive Vice Chairman</p>
